hes in critical condition following a motorcycle accident at 
about noon he has extensive head trauma wise said 
buseys work as the doomed 1950s rock star in the 1978 film the 
buddy holly story earned him an academy award nomination the 
onetime rock n roll musician who like holly was born in texas 
performed his own renditions of holly songs in the film 
